706317f-a.folder: President Street & Van Brunt Street, Brooklyn, NY
706317f-a.original_title: Brooklyn: President Street - Van Brunt Street
706317f-a.text:
21-29 President Street, north side, west of Van Brunt Street; viewed from the S.W. corner. Also shown is Van Brunt Street, west side, north to Harrison Street.

March 27, 1937.

F.L. Speer

707161f-a.original_title: Brooklyn: Van Brunt St. - President St.
707161f-a.text:
